Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens: Mainz Begegnung Christi mit Veronika" addressed to "Prof H G Evers Traisa bei Darmstadt Waldstrasse 43 Germany" dated 11.02.1958

  • Bibliographic references
  • Photo of engravings
  • Journal: "Siegerland im Bild. Tradition und Moderne" dated July 1958
  • Correspondence with Willy Schommer dated 1958
  • Correspondence with Esser dated 1958
  • Correspondence with Franz Roh dated 1957
  • Photos of 'Veronica and Christ bearing the Cross'
  • Photocopy of a reproduction of 'Veronica and Christ bearing the Cross'
  • Invitation to the exhibition: "Ein Grosses Jahrhundert der Malerei. Niederländische Gemälde aud dem Mainzer Museum" dated 1957 with annotations
  • Article: 'Zwei groβe Jahrhunderte der Malerei' in "Darmstädter Echo" dated 30.04.1957
  • Extracts from different publications
  • Draft text "Begegnung Christi mit Veronika"
